{
  "stem": "4686.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were putting together certain houses marked with a-- a yellow star.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were putting the people into it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that was the job of the Jewish council to organize it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They decreed which houses will be Jewish houses, and they had to fit the people in there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then, I volunteered and worked for them, because there was no telephones so much, as a boy on a bicycle who rushes with the messages from here to there, and take notes, and helping organizing that big movement.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In our house, our house became a Jewish house.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And grandma, grandpa moved in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother's parents.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My mother, younger sister, who was still single, and my mother, other young sister with the son-- that's [?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Berge ?] and Peter-- and my mother's brother's wife, Roszi.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Arpad was already in work battalion.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Berge's ?] husband, [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Pali, ?] was in work battalion.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so, in the house where we used to live the four of us, now it was grandma, grandpa, Magda, [?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Berge, ?] Peter, Roszi.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Became 10 of us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Look.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Nice people fit into small places, naturally, it wasn't very convenient.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had-- basically, it was a normal size room, and a very big room, and a kitchen and a bathroom.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was reasonably crowded.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And also, they wanted to empty their homes, so all the furnishing came down.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Luckily, we had big storage area.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because by that time, the factory wasn't working.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So there was all the furnishing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Grandparents had a very nice, big house.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Berge ?] had nice single-bedroom home.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "All this furnishing came down to our place.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And plus our furnishing stayed there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And that's how we started to-- to live and organize the life.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Look.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
